metadata.title: CHALA Wallet Crossbody Cell Phone Purse-Women Faux Leather Multicolor Handbag with Adjustable Strap
features: Efficient, Compact, Easy-To-Carry. Convertible straps make it a pouch, purse, or crossbody
Twist clasp keeps top flap closed. Multiple credit card slots inside.
Made of Faux Leather. Comes with a flower keycharm.
description: The new Wallet Crossbody is here! Versatile, compact, and adorned with a whimsical character! Front slide pocket fits smart phones. Rear slide pocket, zipper pull is a cute star and flower charm, and zips open for large wallet. Lots of slots, ID window, and zip pocket for coins. Convertible straps make it a pouch, purse, or crossbody. Materials: Faux Leather. Color: Black. Dimensions: 5.25"W x 7.5"H x 1.5"D. Strap adjustable: 7"~30" Designed in California, USA. Colors may not be exactly as pictured. Inside lining patterns may vary.
